Metastore
----------------------------------------------------------

	# Meta data such as Table Schema is stored in Metastore #472
	# Can be either embedded derby database (or) MySQL
	# Meta data is never stored in HDFS #489
	
	# 'metastore_db'
		+ For derby, Meta files are stored in the directory 'metastore_db' #473

    # Read more of Metastore service(daemon) & properties here...#482, ##483
    
Warehouse
----------------------------------------------------------
		
   	# For internal tables, Data resides in warehouse(/user/hive/warehouse) #473
   		
	# 'default' database
		+ By Default, all the tables created are stored in 'default' database
		+ 'default' database maps to /user/hive/warehouse
		
    
	
